node.text: Went to the drag strip with the mustang GT and had a great time. Needs boost for sure though!

node.title: Racing A Built Z06 For Fun

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on July 29, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, car and outdoors.

node.text: Knocking Some Bodywork Out!!! This 67 Camaro Is Now Looking Super Official With The Entire Front End On It! Can’t Wait To Slap On Some More Bondo On This Thing And Get It Ready For A Fresh Paint Job! What Color Y’all Thinking?! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on July 27, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, car and outdoors.

node.text: Finally Got This Sucker Welded Up!!! We Threw Down Some Dimes, Nickels And Quarters To Get This Job Done! It Definitely Was Pretty Tough But This Camaro Is Looking Better Than Ever! Can’t Wait To Slap In The New Motor! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on July 25, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and car.

node.text: The Last Of The Damages!!! The 67 Camaro Is Starting To Look Good From This Side! Still Needs A Good Bit Of Work Before We Do Any Body Work But Were Making Great Progress, Also Got Some Epic Engine Swap Parts From @holleyperformance And Here Soon Were Gonna Be Engine Swappin!!! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on July 22, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Huge Headquarters Update!!! We Decided To Take The Day To Do Some Property Maintenance Up On The Mountain Before It Gets Outta Hand! Also We Got Some Pretty Cool Upgrades As Well, Can’t Wait To Show Y’all!!! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on July 20, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, car and road.

node.text: The 67 Camaro SS Is Moving Right Along!!! We Finally Tore Off The Old Quarter Panel And Found Some Crazy Stuff Left Behind By The Previous Repair Man! This Build Is Getting Pretty Real And Were Loving It, Also The Tesla Got Something Special! Can’t Wait To Show Y’all!!! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on July 18, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, car and outdoors.

node.text: Making Some Major Progress On The Camaro Body!!! This Thing Is Starting To Look Super Sick! Although It’s Been Pretty Tough Replacing The Structural Pieces, We’re Still Making It Happen! The Quarter Panel Is Definitely Gonna Be The Real Challenge Though!! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on July 15, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, car and outdoors.

node.text: Finally Got All Of The Parts Needed To Rebuild The Body Of This 1967 Chevrolet Camaro SS!!! Also Everything Was Ordered On Ebay And Came In Pretty Dang Quick! While We Wait On The Parts Needed For The LT4 Engine Swap, Were Gonna Undo These Damages Right Quick! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on July 13, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: Finally Got This Junkyard Engine Yanked Out!!! Can’t Wait To Slap In The Zl1 LT4 Supercharged Engine And Trans In This Thing! Also Got This Thing Rollin Around With It’s Brand New Suspension! Any Other Suggestions??? #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on July 11, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: We’re Back On The 1967 Chevrolet Camaro SS Classic Car Build!!! This Build Is About To Get Wild! We Got The Perfect Doner Car, A 2018 Camaro Zl1!!! 650 Ponies And 650 Torque Bone Stock Should Be Plenty, But You Never Know We Might Pick Those Numbers Up A Bit! Can’t Wait To Show Y’all This Thing!! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on July 08, 2021. May be an image of road.

node.text: Time For A Price Breakdown!!! These Teslas Are Pretty Dang Pricey! This Is Most Likely The Last Video Dedicated To The Tesla Before We Move Onto The Next Thing! So We Decided To End It With A Few More Solid Tests. It’s Gonna Be Epic! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on July 06, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, car and road.

node.text: Just Out Here Putting This Tesla To The Test!!! Finally Got All The Carbon Installed From @cmsttuning And Now We Are Left With A Few Other Aftermarket Parts To Throw On This Thing! This Model X Definitely Puts In Work, Can’t Wait To Show Y’all!! #newvideotoday #goonzquad

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by goonzquad on July 04, 2021. May be an image of car and outdoors.

node.text: Time For The Official Test Drive!!! This 2020 Tesla Model X Has Made It A Long Ways And It Is Looking Better Than Ever! We Ended Up Throwing Our First Few Carbon Parts From @cmsttuning And This Sucker Is Starting To Look Aggressive!!! #newvideotoday #goonzquad
